                                    <h6 className="font-bold text-primary mb-2 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px]">Strategic Insight</h6>
                                    "Your cooling profile is excellent. To reach 'Eco Master' status, consider upgrading Entertainment nodes to Grade-A low-kinetic power sensors."
